  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook chicken breast in a pan with coconut oil until browned and cooked through. Set aside.",
    "In the same pan, add onion, garlic, and Filipino seasoning, and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add sliced bitter gourd and cook until tender.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together casserole bread, crumbly parmesan, and cooked chicken.",
    "Add the bread mixture to the pan and stir until combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 20-25 minutes, or until the top is golden brown.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
